Summary:
--------
The Sentiment Analyzer provides a full pipeline from raw text data to actionable insights. 
It combines data validation, AI inference, results aggregation, and visualization into a 
professional-grade Python application. This workflow can be expanded for larger datasets, 
different transformer models, or integrated into production environments.
